Enum ResponderMethodTypes

    public enum ResponderMethodTypes
extends java.lang.Enum<ResponderMethodTypes>
    Every command that Metro executes must have a strategy defined for how it will execute that command. There are just four strategies for satisfying requests from the metro server. These values have to be entered in the environment configuration XML file
